### Summary of Changes Per File

| File | Lines Changed (approx) | Nature of Change |
|------|----------------------|------------------|
| `useUniverseCamera.js` | ~25 lines | Add `isFlying` ref, `cameraRef`/`zoomRef`, `onComplete` param, interaction guards, unmount cleanup |
| `Universe.jsx` | ~10 lines | Wire flyTo to star clicks with onComplete, add click blocking |
| `StarGroup.jsx` | ~30 lines | Add Group ref, Konva import, useEffect with two-phase Tween |
| `InteractiveLayer.jsx` | 0 lines | No changes needed |

---

### Critical Files for Implementation

- `C:/Users/johnm/iskrib_v3/client/src/components/Universe/hooks/useUniverseCamera.js` - Core flyTo logic: add isFlying ref, onComplete callback, interaction blocking, stable deps via refs
